cc:Work.dc:title: Pink Green Decorative Ribbon
cc:Work.dc:description: This was wasting a way on a century old ad for cancersticks, so I thought I would repurpose it and allow it to be reincarnated here! This could be used as a divider I suppose, but it would look best with a title written on top of the ribbon like a banner. Anyway, rock on little ribbon mice!
